      "term": "apism",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "C2",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "Religious respect or symbolic worship of bees, especially in ancient cultures.",
          "examples": [
            "Some historians believe that apism played a role in certain ancient Egyptian rituals.",
            "The temple decorations suggest a form of apism, where bees were linked to the gods."
